    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape\u2014I've made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it runs like a dream and looks great too! It\u2019s the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
