    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly captures the balance between sophisticated luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous metallic shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a well-loved vehicle used for commuting. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring supple charcoal leather upholstery; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening of the side bolsters, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. Every technological feature, including the high-fidelity sound system, heated seats, and navigation interface, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, backed by a complete folder of service records showing consistent synthetic oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with crisp precision. With 70% tread remaining on the premium all-season tires, this car is turn-key ready for its next owner who values a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term value. This automobile has undergone a comprehensive assessment to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal remain at a high standard. It represents a dependable choice for those seeking a refined driving experience without the premium of a new-market price point. Professionalism and quality are evident in every detail of this offering.",
      "price": 34850.0,
