    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
